OL,6,FA driver who was caught on camera
OL,7,Fcarrying out dangerous manoeuvres in
OL,8,Fhis BMW across Hampshire and Berkshire
OL,9,Fhas been banned from driving for two
OL,10,Fyears.
OL,12,FWilliam Hoy, 23, of Mowbray Hill,
OL,13,FMortimer, was filmed drifting around
OL,14,Froundabouts and pedestrians during a
OL,15,Fseries of incidents between August and
OL,16,FOctober 2024.
OL,18,FPassengers could be seen hung out of
OL,19,Fthe windows on the footage.
